		<title>Use an Interim Management Strategy to Catch Your Competition Napping</title>
		<link>http://cbesondy.wordpress.com/2008/12/09/use-an-interim-management-strategy-to-catch-your-competition-napping/</link>
		<comments>http://cbesondy.wordpress.com/2008/12/09/use-an-interim-management-strategy-to-catch-your-competition-napping/#comments</comments>
