		<title>Employment Outlook Not So Bad</title>
		<link>http://cbesondy.wordpress.com/2008/12/09/employment-outlook-not-so-bad/</link>
		<comments>http://cbesondy.wordpress.com/2008/12/09/employment-outlook-not-so-bad/#comments</comments>
